{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"6e1f99",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Neuromyelitis optica (Devic disease)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"c94760",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Recurrent episodes of longitudinally extensive myelitis and optic neuritis without the brain lesions typical of ",
{
"type":"no-wrap",
"children":[
{
"type":"abbreviation",
"title":"multiple sclerosis",
"children":[
"MS"
]
},
";"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"alert",
"children":[
{
"type":"abbreviation",
"title":"neuromyelitis optica",
"children":[
"NMO"
]
},
"-IgG autoantibody may be present"
]
}
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-3 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"8a7b88",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Idiopathic transverse myelitis"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"488a3a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Subacute onset of weakness, sensory changes, and bowel/bladder dysfunction, typically after a viral infection"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"d228e3",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Distinguished from MS by the presence of complete myelitis, no oligoclonal bands or elevated IgG index in the ",
{
"type":"no-wrap",
"children":[
{
"type":"abbreviation",
"title":"cerebrospinal fluid",
"children":[
"CSF"
]
},
","
]
},
" and no lesions on brain MRI"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-4 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"fa9353",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Vitamin B",
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"sub",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
"12"
]
},
" deficiency"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"463ac8",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Paresthesias, lower-extremity weakness, and gait instability"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"037b4a",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Findings may include paraparesis, vibration and position sense loss, and sensory ataxia."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"8d6b19",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"alert",
"children":[
"Anemia may be absent"
]
},
" "
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
